                    <span>from Marisa D'Vari, author of Building Buzz: How to Reach and Impress Your Target Audience (www.BuildingBuzz.com)<BR>....<BR>What I liked best about Andre's book was reinforcing the often-ignored notion that to most people, you are what you wear. In a simple yet edifying and entertaining voice, she shares valuable success secrets with her readers about how they can project the right image for any business or social situation. Thanks, Mary Lou, for reminding women people have to "see and trust you" before they can really hear and understand you.</span>
                  
